{"tid":1425300,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"影響民生既行動除咗失民意,最大鑊係會增加敵人","createTime":"2019-08-06T17:40:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T17:59:10.000Z","uid":67043,"like":107,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"39fc5c8cb5467f9149cbc824099fbe6bafb9808f","tid":1425300,"uid":67043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:40:14.000Z","msg":"大家要諗一諗2014年係輸係邊？係政府打民生牌，最終支持既人越嚟越少，同時亦樹立越嚟越多敵人，最後輸咗場運動。<br />\n依家政府又想重施故技，所以有幾樣嘢市民大反應既就要轉變做法，例如塞地鐵，交通燈等。其實針對返政府同啲狗既話大家都理解同支持，但攪到啲唔關事既人，反而會多咗敵人。要記住我哋最重要係要贏呢場運動，讓大家可以唔帶口罩係煲底相見，為被拉既手足平反。天琦講過時刻要思考同時都要檢討<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></strong>"},{"pid":"e6333e34c4b580e7110f495caa8bf929ddb0a59d","tid":1425300,"uid":67043,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:48:57.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"a1f49edcef21354708e1a7ede13c3154d48a59f6","tid":1425300,"uid":67043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T18:19:02.000Z","msg":"冇人推雖有再自推啦"},{"pid":"a27a0f65ec7dacbc9db2497efae003acf412d21b","tid":1425300,"uid":67043,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T01:19:27.000Z","msg":"依家個鋪排同2014年尾段一樣，大家仲係忍唔到道氣，唔冷靜一吓，運動輪咗真係乜都冇"},{"pid":"39d0c3790657700e425cf0b3d056e2e2f906ae64","tid":1425300,"uid":67043,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:41:39.000Z","msg":"睇吓天琦信中講乜<br />\n<br />\n我時常提醒自己：<span style=\"color: red;\">政治的工作不只是要令支持自己的人繼續支持自己，而更是要令不支持自己的人轉為支持自己</span>，改變想法，認同自己的方向。<br />\n<br />\n如是者，假如我們希望社會能夠寬容地看待被論定為「暴動」的「暴徒」，理解這些無聲者的訴求，接納這些無權者的諫言，我想，我們<span style=\"color: red;\">必須警惕每一言一行</span>，到底會<span style=\"color: red;\">更接近目標，還是距離更遠呢？</span>"},{"pid":"97c304a84759d9b45f7560d7afbedff26190da72","tid":1425300,"uid":67043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:21:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"235747cf1e251bed6ec010507fc5947cb9c1e6fa","tid":1425300,"uid":67043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T12:58:43.000Z","msg":"冇人推自己推"},{"pid":"223c264a64f3efdd2c33033ce9590e0a0901a978","tid":1425300,"uid":264246,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T12:59:34.000Z","msg":"罷買等同於罷工"},{"pid":"2f2ccaa77750b9a94be830d6648231f61bacb7d3","tid":1425300,"uid":67043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"223c264a64f3efdd2c33033ce9590e0a0901a978","tid":1425300,"uid":264246,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T12:59:34.000Z","msg":"罷買等同於罷工"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T13:01:22.000Z","msg":"要諗埋藍屍會大量買"},{"pid":"0e67d547c21d92d6a99fa401fc666d63db04d174","tid":1425300,"uid":264246,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2f2ccaa77750b9a94be830d6648231f61bacb7d3","tid":1425300,"uid":67043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"223c264a64f3efdd2c33033ce9590e0a0901a978","tid":1425300,"uid":264246,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T12:59:34.000Z","msg":"罷買等同於罷工"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T13:01:22.000Z","msg":"要諗埋藍屍會大量買"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T13:02:14.000Z","msg":"咁咪等佢地買,無所謂"},{"pid":"bddfff46be57457c1f058a60d970dfff6680b3b9","tid":1425300,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T13:04:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0a1c2e0ac50e10d0052cd11b4d9b609e756c5898","tid":1425300,"uid":44171,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T13:05:43.000Z","msg":"呢5年我地咩鳩都無搞啦, 藍屍咪又係有增無減<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"723d3f72ba9ae46d143a796da2d1ff2642651f36","tid":1425300,"uid":189046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T13:07:40.000Z","msg":"阻唔到中共滲透<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01f3ff58f3966d09514e0a14da188083f223510d","tid":1425300,"uid":301467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T13:10:42.000Z","m